  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0bae\u0bc6\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0b89\u0baf\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bae\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0ba4\u0bc7\u0b9a \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0baf \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0b9a\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0b8e\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0ba3\u0bbf - \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb0 \u0bae\u0bc0\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9a\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0bb5\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b86\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0baf\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Meets with top US officials and IMF officials The main opponent - research on measures for economic recovery",
      "author": "Vishnu",
      "body_lines": [
        "Members of the main opposition, led by Sajid Premadasa, met with a group of top US officials and a group of IMF officials today (29) to discuss measures to help the country recover from the current economic crisis.",
        "The US High Level delegation, which includes Robert Cabrot, US Assistant Secretary of State for Asia, and Kelly Gaitling, US Assistant Secretary of State for South and Central Asian Affairs, arrived in the country on Sunday.",
        "The group stayed in Sri Lanka until the 29th and held meetings with a delegation led by President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa, Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe, Leader of the Opposition Sajid Premadasa, economists and representatives of international organizations to discuss ways to help Sri Lanka in the face of a major economic crisis.",
        "Accordingly, a meeting was held on Wednesday between a group of top US officials and a group comprising Sajid Premadasa, leader of the main opposition United People's Force, and party members Harsha de Silva, Kabir Haseem and Eran Wickremaratne.",
        "During the meeting, the Opposition thanked the United States for all assistance provided to Sri Lanka by the victims of the economic crisis and discussed the next steps.",
        "Meanwhile, a meeting between a group of IMF officials in Sri Lanka and members of the United People's Power took place yesterday.",
        "It is noteworthy that the economic situation of the country and the reforms that need to be carried out in anticipation of the economic recovery were discussed."
      ],
